    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个剑与魔法的世界，一个包罗万象的城市，你是一个被迫继承了酒馆的新手老板，前方有艰难的路等着你。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28天的期限，你需要利用好手中的一切来赚钱，每次游戏你都会遇到不同的人，买到不同的装备，获得不同的特权。运用好他们的特性并合理搭配组合，能让你从沉重的债务中找到生机，甚至突破所有人的期望成为一代酒馆大亨也说不定。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需手动布置位置，你可以直接装点好酒馆的装饰，增添酒馆的人气，让顾客络绎不绝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras/a0a804c7480ccaab17c180f629292653.avif?t=1762711575\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras_big/a0a804c7480ccaab17c180f629292653.avif?t=1762711575 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同职业和品级的员工，各自都掌握着与众不同的技能，他们是让酒馆繁荣起来的关键。员工们也有着丰富多彩的身世和故事，每个人都值得深交。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras/b330d1e265a924f1e63f17ea85e10c2c.avif?t=1762711575\" width=616 height=353 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上百种食材、料理和饮品，你需要精心安排酒馆的菜单，有时菜谱也不是越多越好哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras/9b4dd0c0b4ff58fa8046b2a1e48cbfdb.avif?t=1762711575\" width=616 height=353 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店和公会系统帮助你获得各式各样的装备道具，还能举办活动获得增益，完成任务来获得额外的奖励，还有更多机制隐藏在员工身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras/50d47ff185824ab125f351b416ec916f.avif?t=1762711575\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100580/extras/5c9a559ce7fe1e78f87743fad842fad3.avif?t=1762711575\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白影酒馆既是生意，也是生活。无论你想寻找什么，都可以来这里坐一坐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取更多资讯，反馈游戏问题，欢迎加入官方QQ群：976944204</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小红书：tavernrevisited</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微博、b站：流浪狗工作室</p>",
